name: BLUE RAGE EDITON BY ADAEZE OKARO

metadata.name: Blue Rage.
metadata.description:
Welcome to the first open edition experience by portrait, fashion and fine art photographer Adaeze Okaro.

The many faces of uncertainty, confusion & loss were pivotal in creating the piece "Blue Rage''.  
The feeling of seeing your life at a long halt and really not knowing what to do next. Just you, your mind, body and life in the deafening dark.  
For her, every emotion has a color it associates itself with. And the color she believed would beautifully portray the feeling of self anger, passion and rage was blue.  
In what color do you identify your rage?
